@node Main "Ixim - Documentation"

                               'Ixim' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Ixim' is a @{"Workbench game" link play} where you have to place various bars
so that they make a symmetrical pattern on an 'X' shaped game
board.

  The game starts with a number of unmoveable horizontal and
diagonal bars that are randomly placed. By clicking on these bars,
other -moveable- bars will randomly appear or disappear. If you
click on a moveable bar, that bar will disappear and reappear at
another location... or return at the place it was located...

  Complete the game in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

